com.b2international.snowowl.snomed

Interface Relationship

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Annotatable, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, Component, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RelationshipImpl

    public interface Relationship
extends Component, Annotatable
    Representation of a SNOMED CT relationship. Represents some kind of association between two SNOMED CT concepts.

    The following features are supported:

    • Group
    • Union Group
    • Destination Negated
    • Source
    • Destination
    • Type
    • Characteristic Type
    • Modifier
    • Refinability Ref Set Members

    See Also:
    SnomedPackage.getRelationship()
